A cozy, bustling tavern scene filled with joyful Kithkin, a small, cheerful, humanoid race; the central figure is a lively Kithkin bard perched on a table, mid-song, raising a tankard with revelers around her laughing and toasting; colorful banners and lanterns hang overhead, musicians play in the background, and the mood is festive and inviting; the overall style is warm, vibrant, and detailed to capture the merriment and camaraderie of the setting.